<td colspan=3 class=black><br><p><font class=b>How to play</font><br>
You are the commander of a mobile early-warning defense base - our solar system's last defense against alien invasion. You must destroy the incoming missiles before they destroy your radar stations.<br><br>
Move the MOUSE to aim the defense missiles, click the LEFT MOUSE BUTTON to fire.<br><br>
Once all your radar bases are destroyed, there is no hope for us on Earth. Good luck, commander. You are our last hope!<br><br>
<font class=b>Tips:</font><br>
- Don't waste your missiles as you have a limited stockpile.<br>
- On later levels, concentrate your defense around one or two bases.<br>
- Press S to turn the sound effects on and off and M to turn the music on and off.<br>
- Press P to toggle the game pause.<br><br>





























































